<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=1440">
    <title>BABATHE.COM</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/library.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/common.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/templateA.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/templateB.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/templateC.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/templateD.css">
    <script src="../js/library.js"></script>
    <script src="../js/layout.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="wrap">
        <header></header>
        <section class="container"> 
            <div class="login-wrap">
                <div>
                    <div class="form-area w-half">
                        <h2 class="page-title">로그인<span class="font-s20">로그인하시고 할인 및 쿠폰 등 바바더닷컴의<br>다양한 회원 혜택을 만나보세요.</span></h2>                    
                        <div class="form-wrap">
                            <div class="form-row">
                                <div class="form-box">
                                    <input type="text" value="" id="login1-1" placeholder="아이디 입력 (이메일 주소 또는 휴대폰 번호)"/>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-row">
                                <div class="form-box">
                                    <input type="password" value="" id="login1-2" placeholder="비밀번호 입력"/>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-row">
                                <div class="w-half">
                                    <div class="checkbox"><input type="checkbox" id="auto-login"><label for="auto-login" class="font-s16">자동 로그인</label></div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="w-half">
                                    <a href="#" class="tx-link">아이디 찾기 · 비밀번호 찾기</a>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <button type="button" class="btn lg primary mg-t-40">로그인</button>
                        </div>
                        <div class="sns-login">
                            <a href="#" class="naver">네이버</a>
                            <a href="#" class="kakao">카카오</a>
                            <a href="#" class="facebook">페이스북</a>
                            <a href="#" class="insta">인스타그램</a>
                        </div>
                        <div class="no-member">
                            <a href="#">비회원 주문 조회</a>
                            <p>비회원으로 구매하실 경우 쿠폰 사용 및 포인트 적립 등의<br>혜택을 받으실 수 없습니다.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="w-half">
                        <div style="background:rgba(222,222,222,.3); width:340px; height:495px; margin-top:65px; text-align:center;">회원혜택 영역</div>
                        <a href="#" class="btn primary w-full">회원가입</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <footer></footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>